description:
Blobufo Platformer Game with Diffrent Mechanic on Space!

Our character moves with the power splash from his weapon.
Complete the levels in this space without hitting the enemies and Thorns!
Don't look easy! Seriously hard!
Do you think it would be easy to move through space and pass the creatures? No!

Features;
Diffrent Platformer Gameplay,
15 Completable Challenging Levels,
Enemies and
Galaxy!
name: Blobufo
